actionStep.description: There are lots of group strength training classes, and they can be a fun way to get fit. Take time today to think about your interests, goals, and the type of class that might work for you. Do you crave a high-intensity workout, like boot-camp? Are you looking for the core focus of a Pilates class? Or do you want to learn how to use free weights?
actionStep.completionText: Getting strong can be fun—and social too!
